Actions.Text: REFERRED TO COMMERCE, ECONOMIC DEVELOPMENT AND SMALL BUSINESS

Title: Relates to establishing a nonprofit news media jobs grant program
Summary: Establishes a nonprofit news media jobs grant program within the newspaper and broadcast media jobs program to provide grants to support certain nonprofit media organizations which increase employees.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the economic development law, in relation to the newspaper and broadcast media jobs program
